{{Infobox_NPC |name = Heath |image = Heath.png |personality = |time_active = Anytime after ''[[The Castle Guard]]'' |gender = Male |race = |age = 7th Term |location = [[Syra Hovering Reefs]] ([[Fort O'Virbus]]) }} '''Heath''' is a NPC in {{XC3}}.
== Overview == Heath can be found in [[Fort O'Virbus]]. He is the captain of the Soltnar Squad of the [[Keves Castle]] Guard, and has a rivalry with [[Wynonna]] of the Khatorl Squad. He has a more emotional view of combat, causing tension with the more objective Wynonna. {{clr}}
